Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西怪怪的  我不知為啥有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視中正在播放的  是跟我一點關係都沒有的同縣選手的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥我正支持著正處於落後的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又不知為啥覺得差不多春日要搞點事出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點整全員在車站前集合  老老實實地過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一句話都沒說上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你說帶東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套泳裝  還有足夠的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一定要騎自行車來  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像又知道春日打算要說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說  是感覺之前好像出現過完全相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的「既視感」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虛！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿點幹勁出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  全都到齊了  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天要有夏天的樣子  不能不做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就要行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個只有一次的高一的暑假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便我們是用自行車去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也騎來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行車只有你和我的兩輛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可能好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  可不能輸給古泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  接下來是要玩啊  你怎麼就筋疲力盡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的錯啊  誰的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這消毒液的氣味  真給人一種實在的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  來游泳吧  比賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就讀不懂這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊過來  水溫溫的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來挺歡樂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很歡樂的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得  涼宮同學也學會了有常識性的娛樂方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得那麼開心的涼宮同學  是不會做什麼震動這個世界的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:04:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  大概是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春以來發生了種種事情的緣故  只是變得有點神經質了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們也去游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是市民泳池  倒是個更適合平民泳池這名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這種景象以前也見到過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥覺得長門好像有些無聊的樣子  在那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  然後春日跑來  說了這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個就是我的團員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼他們都會聽的  所以隨便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩水中足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這種事也常有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既視感什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦  實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著考慮了下今後的活動計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣來度過已經所剩無幾的暑假的計劃表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假只剩下兩週了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得還有很多事情沒做呢  但時間卻只剩那麼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以聽好了  接下來要一起都做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠有什麼想要做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  這附近什麼地方有盂蘭盆會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煙火匯演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了撈金魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是實玖瑠的強烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼阿虛  明天開始實行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（來電  涼宮春日）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  將我的懶覺奪走的又是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是說找到盂蘭盆會的會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  地點是市民運動場…的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  實玖瑠和有希都說沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以接下來去買今晚要穿的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有  又找到了買一整套的話就會便宜的店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也陪著來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日進了女裝的大賣場之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自為朝比奈學姐和長門挑選了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後毫不客氣地衝進了試衣間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我們等了大約一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都伸懶腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人終於都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都非常合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  是我給挑選的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  真不愧是我挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐  好棒  朝比奈學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧得能聚集起這麼多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該是很久沒來了  卻覺得最近就來過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個樓塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個攤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有你想要玩的撈金魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去玩吧  如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對那種東西有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？我給你買
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為啥有種受她照顧的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西由我來買就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  大豐收啊大豐收  十三條
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不需要那麼多  就和實玖瑠一人只要了一條
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有希  你那面具哪裡搞來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背借我用下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  轉過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來玩煙火吧  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道「吃飯只吃八分飽」這俗語嗎  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是夏天  在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  雖然極力想要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情卻讓我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位  明天是捉昆蟲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的蟲子最多的那個人  就把團長的權力讓給他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  雖說玩也沒問題  你暑假作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊  那樣的作業有三天不就全部做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種麻煩事就得事先趕緊收拾掉  再毫無後顧之憂地玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是正確的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種傢伙腦子這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  是個讓人有種「連這也是啊」的感覺的大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰  就在這樣的天氣中舉辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各人都以自己的方式進行了奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說不出所料還是說啥呢  獲勝者是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  我們在還沒搞清狀況的狀態下就被召集了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同樣一無所知的情況下被套上了青蛙的罩衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始在超市的門口發氣球的兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還以為要死了  不如說就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了  這麼熱的天真是辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長大叔也謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在實玖瑠的份上說送給我們當作工錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就為了這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  你想什麼時候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  奪去了我的安眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是朝比奈學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有非常不好的事情…這樣下去我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會跟朝比奈學姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點情況  你能現在就過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問麼！我馬上就去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了未來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說回不去了  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  事情是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在重複同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在重複同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在重複同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  沒有比現在更清楚的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才和朝比奈學姐談了下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是叫上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後意識到最近這裡時間的流動出現了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該說是朝比奈學姐的功績吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託她的福我也確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正無數次重複體驗同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個剛才就聽你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說應該是八月十七日到三十一日之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處在這永無止境的暑假的正中間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  確實是無止境的狀態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是個不會完結的Endless Summer呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個世界裡  九月一日之後的時間全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐無法回到未來也是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法回到不存在的未來  這是理所當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  這麼莫名其妙的話哪裡理所當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要誰相信那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望至少你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…也由我來說明一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為禁止說明的事項  我一直在和未來聯絡和做禁止說明的事項
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個禮拜左右沒有禁止說明的事項了啊  有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正這麼想著  於是禁止說明的事項…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:30.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我嚇了一大跳  慌張之下就做了禁止說明的事項…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但也完全是禁止說明的事項…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈學姐  難道說那個禁止說明的事項是放送禁止用語什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我們被困在那個叫什麼封閉空間裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一部分的時間被分割開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到八月三十一日二十四時整的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被重置  再回到十七日的過程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  全人類的記憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也會重置  會從頭再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是關於時間這個那個了的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  那也是沒辦法的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這件事和朝比奈學姐沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是涼宮同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她本人沒有意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心裡什麼地方總在想著暑假不要結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還留有什麼遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她是想著暑假還有什麼事情剩下沒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個會把一些莫名其妙的事情\N展開到大宇宙規模的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始我就有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像樂在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近頻繁發生的既視感之謎終於解開了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來  那只能理解為是由於記憶重置而散落下來的殘渣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也察覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人都感覺得到這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你算是特例了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有和涼宮同學親近的人才能感覺到這份異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那春日怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙多少有一點意識到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說有了反而糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  別說是既視感了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該有一個人保存著所有輪迴中的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說也該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…全都記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶問下  到底重複幾次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是第15499次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15499？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15499是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你在說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那話是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多的次數  我們全都在重複同樣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非全部如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15499次中沒有去盂蘭盆會的模式  有第2391次和第11054次的這兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  去了盂蘭盆會而沒有撈金魚的模式有437次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工的有9026次  其內容分成6個部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了發放氣球  還有搬貨物  收銀  發送傳單  接電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我知道了  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15499次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門她這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上兩週的話就是…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是594年的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼長的時間僅她一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠好好地保留著記憶  無數次無數次地重複嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門  你到底到現在為止都以什麼樣的心情度過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又聽了荒唐的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天是觀測天體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是長門公寓的樓頂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天體望遠鏡由古泉準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找UFO吧  UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春日別…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要啊  要壞掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底想做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能搞清楚的話問題也就迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試下這樣怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面突然抱住涼宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她耳邊輕語「I love you」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這由誰來做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你沒有適合的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我斷然拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來做怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的了  我做這角色還不夠格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會讓涼宮同學增加多餘的混亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒濤般的暑假活動消化體制還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去了打擊中心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了貨真價實的煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加了垂釣大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有試膽大會  看連場電影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水浴  打保齡球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及唱卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在活動來活動去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我不認為這樣春日就會滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此也沒有什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此暑假的日子也一天天減少著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼過著  日子到了八月三十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣課題就如實地完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  還有什麼想做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假已經做了好多事了  已經很充實了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  春日  你應該還沒有滿足才對  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天當預備日先空下來了  大家就這樣休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天再在社團教室再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  這既視感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還前所未有地強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣讓春日回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重複了一萬幾千次的兩星期又要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我該做什麼呢  應該說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春日的話裡應該有提示的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  也想不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業  還沒動過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢  怎麼都成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再重複的話  作業做了也沒意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管明天來不來  到時候就交給那時的我算啦


